cess, educating you about the system, addressing your concerns, and strategizing on your behalf.</p>\n<p>When you need a trusted criminal defense attorney in Orange County, Farris Law Firm is ready to help you move forward with confidence.</p>\n<h2>About Our&nbsp;Orange County Criminal Defense Lawyers</h2>\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 1.71429rem; margin-bottom: 1.71429rem; font-size: 1.28571rem;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1886\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/service-image-new.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"471\" height=\"547\"></h2>\n<p>Founded by Orange County Criminal Defense Lawyer Charles and his wife, Beatrice, in 2024, Farris Law Firm introduces a refreshing approach to criminal law in Southern California.</p>\n<p>Having managed thousands of misdemeanor and felony cases at other leading firms, they wanted to create a firm that emphasizes client education, a luxurious concierge service, and supportive yet assertive legal advocacy.</p>\n<p>Our firm’s philosophy centers on avoiding scare tactics and high-pressure sales methods. Instead, we opt for clear communication and dedicated five-star service.</p>\n<p>In contrast to the high-volume caseloads typical of large Orange County firms, we intentionally limit the number of cases we take on to focus intently on each client’s needs.</p>\n<p>Our close proximity to the courthouse ensures ease of access and bolsters our local practice, enabling us to nurture strong relationships with judges, prosecutors, and court staff. This relational approach empowers us to guide clients efficiently through the complexities of the criminal justice system without resorting to aggressive tactics that often prove counterproductive.</p>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"info-content\">\n <div class=\"info-image\">\n <img srcset=\"/wp-content/uploads/info-image-new-mobile.webp 768w, /wp-content/uploads/info-image-new.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/info-image-new.webp\" alt=\"Description\">\n </div>\n\n <h2>Comprehensive&nbsp;Criminal Defense Services in Orange County</h2>\n<p>At Farris Law Firm, we handle a broad spectrum of criminal defense cases.</p>\n<p>Whether you’re facing charges related to gun possession, drug offenses, DUIs, or traffic violations such as driving on a suspended license or hit-and-run, our team of Orange County criminal defense lawyers is here to provide support.</p>\n<p>We understand the gravity of these situations and work diligently to ensure your rights are protected at every stage.</p>\n<p>In addition to criminal defense, we offer services in:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Expungement</strong>: Are you looking to clear your criminal record? Our team can guide you through the expungement process, helping you move forward with a clean slate. Expungement can open up new opportunities for employment and personal growth, removing the burden of a past conviction.</li>\n<li><strong>Seal of Arrest and Court Records:</strong>&nbsp;Even if you were never brought to court, or if your case was dismissed, the record of your arrest and the records of your case may still be uncovered during a background check. Our team can help seal these records in many situations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Accessible and Transparent Legal Support from Your&nbsp;Orange County Criminal Defense Lawyer&nbsp;is What You Deserve</h3>\n<p>At Farris Law Firm, our mission is to guide and support you, not intimidate. As your trusted Orange County criminal defense lawyer team, we provide clear, open communication and take the time to understand your perspective, rather than simply accepting law enforcement narratives.</p>\n<p>Our team is highly skilled at negotiating favorable plea deals, but we are equally prepared to take your case to trial if necessary. We are dedicated to providing meaningful value in every defense we handle. If we cannot make a difference in your case, we will be upfront and honest; we won’t take it.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <img class=\"watermark\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/about_watermark2.png\">\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"services\">\n <div class=\"services-image fadeInLeft animate\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/service-image-new.webp\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <div class=\"services-info\">\n <h2>Why Choose Our Criminal Defense Attorneys?</h2>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <h3>\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-auto-scroll=\"true\" data-close-siblings=\"true\">\n <span>We Know Orange County:</span>\n </button>\n </h3>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Our office is only a few minutes down the highway from Harbor Justice Center, located in beautiful Aliso Viejo. We are within easy driving distance of all four Orange County criminal courthouses. We maintain an unmatched network of professional relationships that benefit our clients, and we are deeply familiar with local court rules and the personnel involved in your case, from the prosecutor to the judge.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <h3>\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-auto-scroll=\"true\" data-close-siblings=\"true\">\n <span>Personalized Attention:</span>\n </button>\n </h3>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Unlike high-volume firms, we take on a limited number of cases to ensure each client receives the focused and detailed attention they deserve. This approach allows us to tailor our strategies to the unique circumstances of your case, offering a truly personalized defense.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <h3>\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-auto-scroll=\"true\" data-close-siblings=\"true\">\n <span>Client-Centered Approach:</span>\n </button>\n </h3>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Our firm prides itself on educating and empowering clients throughout the legal process. We prioritize your understanding and involvement in your defense strategy, ensuring you are never left in the dark about the progress and direction of your case.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <h3>\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-auto-scroll=\"true\" data-close-siblings=\"true\">\n <span>No Pressure Tactics:</span>\n </button>\n </h3>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>We believe in transparent communication and avoid scare tactics. Our goal is to provide you with a clear understanding of your options so you can make informed decisions. We are committed to building trust with our clients, guided by honesty and integrity.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <h3>\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-auto-scroll=\"true\" data-close-siblings=\"true\">\n <span>Proven Success Stories:</span>\n </button>\n </h3>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Our track record speaks volumes about our commitment to client success. From reduced charges to case dismissals, we have achieved favorable outcomes for numerous clients, demonstrating our dedication to achieving the best possible results.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"cases\">\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <div class=\"cases-heading\">\n <h2>Get <em>Real</em> Answers from a <em>Real</em> OC Criminal Defense Lawyer</h2>\n <div class=\"case-accordions\">\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" tabindex=\"0\">What should I do if the police arrest me in Orange County?</button>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>If you are arrested, remain calm and request to speak with a criminal defense lawyer from Farris Law Firm. You do not have to say anything during the arrest process. If you’re unable to speak with a lawyer at the moment, call us as soon as possible after the fact.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" tabindex=\"0\">How can an Orange County criminal defense lawyer help me?</button>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Our team will use everything at our disposal to attempt to have the case dismissed, negotiate a favorable plea deal, or proceed to jury trial if necessary. It is our job to help you navigate what may be one of the worst experiences of your life - we assist you in moving past this with minimal damage to your career, family, and finances.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" tabindex=\"0\">Can my criminal record be expunged?</button>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>Yes, your criminal record can be \"expunged\" or in other words \"erased\" in certain circumstances. Arrest and court records can also be sealed. Our team will give you a free consultation to explain all of your options.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n <button class=\"accordion-item-title\" tabindex=\"0\">How do I schedule a consultation with Farris Law Firm?</button>\n <div class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n <p>To discuss your case with our award-winning Orange County criminal defense attorneys, call our office at (818) 861-0861 or click “Schedule a Free Consultation” on our website. We're ready to listen and offer the legal support you need. Your initial consultation is an opportunity to explore your legal options and gain clarity on the next steps - and it costs nothing. You have nothing to lose by calling to get answers today.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <h4>ARE YOU FACING CRIMINAL CHARGES?</h4>\n<h2>Farris Law Firm Can Help You</h2>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"cases-holder\">\n <div class=\"cases-column\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:37px; height:41px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_dui_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_dui_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/dui/\">DUI</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>DUI charges carry severe penalties in California, and having a DUI on your record can negatively impact your license, insurance, education, and career.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:56px; height:35px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_guns_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_guns_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/guns/\">Guns</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>California’s gun laws are strict, and simply carrying a firearm without the requisite permit can land you in criminal court. Even with a valid permit, if you are carrying a weapon and don’t follow every local rule, you could land in hot water.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:53px; height:50px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_domestic_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_domestic_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/domestic-violence/\">Domestic Violence</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>Circumstances that lead to domestic violence charges often are not as straightforward as they initially seem, and alleged abusers will have strong defenses in many cases.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:55px; height:52px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_theft_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_theft_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/theft/\">Theft</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>We represent individuals charged with theft and other property crimes—from shoplifting to robbery.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"cases-column\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:41px; height:42px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_drugs_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_drugs_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/drugs/\">Drugs</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>We represent individuals facing all types of drug charges, from the use and distribution of controlled substances to underage possession of marijuana.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:47px; height:41px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_assault_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_assault_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/assault/\">Assault</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>In California, assault charges carry fines and jail time. If you’ve been charged with assault, you need experienced legal representation.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:48px; height:44px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_vandalism_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_vandalism_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/vandalism/\">Vandalism</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>Vandalism charges can lead to serious consequences under California law, especially if the property damage is over a certain limit. If you’ve been charged with vandalism. We can help.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-item\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-block\">\n <div class=\"card-cases-icon fadeInUp animate\" style=\"width:30px; height:44px;\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_special_new.png\" alt=\"/wp-content/uploads/icon_special_new.png\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-cases-info\">\n <h3 class=\"h3\">\n <a class=\"no-underline\" href=\"/military-diversion/\">Special Services</a> </h3>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"card-cases-text\">\n <p>We also handle cases involving pretrial diversion, bench warrant recalls, military diversion, Veterans Court, and charges against non-California residents.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"cases-link\">\n <a class=\"button\" href=\"/criminal-defense/\">All Practice Areas</a>\n </div>\n \n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"charges lazy-bg\" data-all-bg=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/wp-content/themes/paperstreet/images/charges-bg.jpg\">\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <div class=\"charges-item\">\n <div class=\"charges-image\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/charge-img1-new.webp\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"charges-info\">\n <h3 class=\"animate\">Misdemeanor Charges Carry <span>Serious Consequences</span></h3>\n\n <p>Most often, our Orange County criminal defense lawyers represent individuals facing local misdemeanor charges. While misdemeanors might not be as serious as felonies, convictions can still have life-altering consequences.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"charges-item\">\n <div class=\"charges-image\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/charge-img2-new.webp\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"charges-info\">\n <h3 class=\"animate\">We Can Help You <span>Avoid These Consequences</span></h3>\n\n <p>Regardless of the facts of your case, you have defense options available. From challenging the State’s evidence against you to seeking pretrial diversion (which can eventually lead to dismissal without prosecution), you may have various options for minimizing the consequences of your arrest.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"charges-item\">\n <div class=\"charges-image\">\n <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/charge-img3-new.webp\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"charges-info\">\n <h3 class=\"animate\">Hiring An Experienced Defense Attorney <span>Is The First Step</span></h3>\n\n <p>Hiring an experienced defense lawyer is the first step toward determining how best to approach your case. At Farris Law Firm, we have the experience to help you feel confident in your decision-making and execute your defense strategy effectively.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <img class=\"watermark\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/watermark_white.png\">\n </div>\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"consultation\">\n <div class=\"consultation-image\">\n <img class=\"lazy-img\" data-all-src=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/wp-content/themes/paperstreet/images/consultation-map.webp\" alt=\"map with orange and los angeles counties\">\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <div class=\"consultation-info\">\n <h2>Farris Law Firm | Your Trusted Orange County Criminal Defense Lawyer Team</h2>\n<p>At Farris Law Firm, we stand by you in challenging times, providing trusted criminal defense services in Orange County that put your needs first. Our team acts as your advocate and partner, guiding you through the legal system with confidence, clarity, and assurance.</p>\n<p>Contact us today to speak with an experienced Orange County criminal defense lawyer and learn how we can protect your rights and your future.</p>\n<h2>Schedule a Free Consultation About Your Criminal Case</h2>\n<h3>Talk to an experienced Orange County criminal defense lawyer today</h3>\n<p>If you are facing criminal charges anywhere in Orange County or Los Angeles, we strongly encourage you to contact us for more information. It’s free to speak with an experienced criminal defense lawyer, so you have no risk – call today and get answers to your questions.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"connect\">\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <div class=\"connect-holder\">\n <div class=\"connect-info\">\n <h2>Call Farris first</h2>\n\n <h4>TALK TO US ABOUT YOUR CRIMINAL CASE</h4>\n </div>\n\n <div class=\"connect-number\">\n <a href=\"tel:+1-818-861-0861\">818-861-0861</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n\n \n <section class=\"testimonial lazy-bg\" data-all-bg=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/wp-content/themes/paperstreet/images/testimonial.jpg\">\n <div class=\"row-wide\">\n <div class=\"columns\">\n <h2>Testimonials</h2>\n\n <div class=\"js-card-testimonials testimonial-block\">\n <div class=\"card-testimonial\">\n <div class=\"slide card-testimonial-block\">\n <p></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">My case was a little complicated because I was charged with two DUIs back to back. Charles was in charge for my second one and that one was...</span></p>\n <span><i>A. Auerbach</i></span>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-testimonial\">\n <div class=\"slide card-testimonial-block\">\n <p></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazing work! From start to finish everything was so smooth and easy, Charles Farris made this case so easy and even though my case took...</span></p>\n <span><i>G. Weins</i></span>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"card-testimonial\">\n <div class=\"slide card-testimonial-block\">\n <p></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I’ve had multiple attorneys represent me in my life, but Charles handled things a bit differently. Not only is he patient and...</span></p>\n <span><i>J. Rogers</i></span>\n </div>\n </div>\